===   Chat Everywhere 1.0.0 released ======================

10/02/2003, A. de Bernis : added a buffered output (data was sent one byte
                           after one byte!)
            A. de Bernis : added capabilities reporting (language, version, ...)

10/10/2003, A. de Bernis : added a "StartChatWith" applet parameter to
                           automatically start a private chat upon login
                           (thanks to djlyon for the idea!)

07/10/2003, A. de Bernis : added a Catalan translation
                           (thanks to Alfons!)

06/10/2003, A. de Bernis : added a Spanish translation (thanks Carlos!)


